 number of escrow agents.  Using +for XOR, SK for the escrowed key, and A and B for two random bitstrings, hand SK+A+B, SK+A, and SK+B to three escrow agents.  It ispossible to come with an encoding scheme to match any escrow pattern,for example 3 of 4, such that fewer cooperating escrow agents givesthe cracking agency no benefit.--Robert I. Eachuswith Standard_Disclaimer;use  Standard_Disclaimer;function Message (Text: in Clever_Ideas) return Better_Ideas is...
