c domain" are different for ITAR purposes, so ifyou've got a good enough lawyer who'll do your case for free afterthey've confiscated everything you own as evidence, you might win.But nobody wants to go first, since the stakes are _quite_ high.)--#Pray for peace;      Bill# Bill Stewart 1-908-949-0705 wcs@anchor.att.com AT&T Bell Labs 4M312 Holmdel NJ#              No, I'm *from* New Jersey, I only *work* in cyberspace....# White House Commect Line 1-202-456-1111  fax 1-202-456-2461
